<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Aerial deployed mines -->
  <BDGW_Mines.label>ADM空布雷</BDGW_Mines.label>
  <!-- EN: Aerial deployed mines are proximity mines made extremely simple to fit in shells, thus they lack any proper friend and foe identification system and have a risk of self-detonation after half a year. Your colonist and animals are more likely to accidently trigger them, and it's never safe to deconstruct one, leaving alone the fact They blend in the terrain so well that you can't select them, and they're buried in the ground so bullets can't harm them.\n\nTo safely disarm an ADM, you'll need to use incendiary weapons to ignite the mine, or simply blow'em up with explosives like HE or thermobaric shells.\n\nWith more than level 4 in crafting and intelletual. and not severely impaired visually and manipulatively, you can also attempt to safely disarm an ADM, getting a detached ADM back if succeeds.\n(Faliure of mine disposal or lack of skill will result in explosive consequences)\nAn hostile ADM can be disabled by an EMP blast, then attempt to disarm it in time. -->
  <BDGW_Mines.helpText>ADM空布雷是一种为了塞进炮弹而极其小型化的感应地雷，虽然能极其快捷方便的布撒一片雷区，但是由于不太可靠的敌我识别和仅仅半年的额定工作寿命(超过这个寿命的地雷可能会随时自爆，哪怕并没有被触发)，这样一片雷区对自己人也是潜在的威胁。\n\n由于其埋在地下且尺寸极小，所以无法被玩家选中，也不会被子弹伤害，但是爆炸，范围EMP冲击或者燃烧弹火焰都能引爆ADM地雷，如果有排雷需求可以考虑使用AOE武器攻击可能有地雷的区域。\n\n如果你有一个小人的智识与手工高于4，而且操作与视力没大问题的话，可以尝试安全排除地上的ADM，成功率与智识，手工，视力与操作正相关。如果成功的话会得到一颗ADM地雷。\n智识或手工低于4或者一次失败的尝试会触发地雷。\n敌对的ADM空布雷在你接近的时候就会爆炸，但是可以用EMP攻击来暂时使其失效从而安全拆除。</BDGW_Mines.helpText>
  
</LanguageData>